verbose_text: Of note, when the H 2 O 2 -exposed SH-SY5Y cells were incubated with SB203580 alone, the expression of alpha-synuclein was attenuated compared with the H 2 O 2 group, and incubation of the cells with SB203580, H 2 O 2 and AS-IV (200 mumol/l) together also decreased the expression of alpha-synuclein.
